1
00:00:02,731 --> 00:00:07,731
EMBODIED. Egocentric multimodal Marine training simulator.

2
00:00:07,733 --> 00:00:12,733
LOGCOM training modernization: instructor-to-trainee ratio is the bottleneck.

3
00:00:12,735 --> 00:00:17,735
Eight egocentric scenarios — doorway, checkpoint, casualty, IED, night perimeter.

4
00:00:17,737 --> 00:00:23,737
Each scenario is anchored to a doctrine reference — MCWP, MCRP, TM. No invention.

5
00:00:23,742 --> 00:00:30,742
Trainee types their action. Multimodal coach reads the frame plus the response.

6
00:00:26,319 --> 00:00:33,319
Vision-capable model classifies the action against doctrine. Structured JSON.

7
00:00:30,831 --> 00:00:37,831
Score, doctrine cite, simulated consequence, coaching feedback — in one shot.

8
00:00:37,833 --> 00:00:43,833
After-action across attempts — a one-page Egocentric Decision Brief.

9
00:00:43,347 --> 00:00:50,347
Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — same code, trainee video stays inside the wire.

10
00:00:50,350 --> 00:00:58,350
Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
